  "body": "Components like `StatusIconTabButton` (#2451) and `StatusNavigationButton` (#2295) can have a badge to render additional information:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"163\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-04-27 at 16 08 27\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/445106/116255724-cf3e2980-a772-11eb-8b4b-3d89c2415212.png\">\r\n\r\nThis should be put in a `StatusBadge` component for reusability.\r\n\r\n### API Proposal:\r\n\r\n```\r\nStatusBadge {\r\n  value: 30\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt can have no `value` as well, in which case the badge is empty and acts more like an indicator:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"58\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-04-27 at 16 09 53\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/445106/116255946-03b1e580-a773-11eb-9296-1280fe723025.png\">\r\n",
